  <summary>10/23/1997--Introduced.
Requires executive branch agencies to annually: (1) review the costs of service contracts; (2) carry out cost comparisons with respect to certain service contracts; and (3) submit a report to the Congress on the results of the review and on the cost comparisons carried out.</summary>
